data.description: Peaceful country setting on 1.3 acres with an additional 2 acres available. Located next to State land minutes away from downtown Lowell. Come home to your oasis in the City and relax by the in-ground pool. An extra large family room with a gas fireplace gives way to beautiful sun room overlooking the yard and pool.  The front of the home features a wrap around screened in porch for relaxing and taking in all nature has to offer. Convenient main floor living includes the master bedroom with a 1/ 2 bath, a second bedroom, another full bathroom and laundry. Two additional bedrooms are upstairs.  The main floor bathroom offers a tub as well as a handicapped accessible shower.  All of this in a location that is nestled between the city of Lowell and State land.
